name: Quick Thumbnail
description:
Figma is very useful and great, but the thumbnail is a little boring, so we made a file to quickly generate the thumbnail.

Step 1. Choose a thumbnail you like.
Step 2. Copy it into your file, modify the title, time, version number.
Step 3. Set it as the thumbnail.

Thanks to Twemoji and Open Peeps!

Design by Nether,Ryan Jyu,Josh
